The '''Insurrection of Iliabath''' was an insurrection in the vicinity of the [[Iliabath system/Legends|Iliabath system]] sometime before [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. The victors of the conflict gave the [[Amulet of Kalara]] as a gift to [[Stonias Leem]] on [[Drewwa]].

